headline.main: TURKS, NAZIS AGREE ON TRADE EQUALITY; Exchange to Be Made in Turkey -- Germany to Get No Grain

lead_paragraph: ANKARA, Turkey, Oct. 15 -- Numan Menemencioglu, the Turkish Under-Secretary for Foreign Affairs, disclosed that the new Turkish-German trade agreement went into effect the day it was signed in Ankara six days ago.
